WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
The following content is a work of fiction. Any resemblance to anyone, living or dead, is coincidental.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.000
The following content is a work of fiction. Any resemblance to anyone, living or dead, is coincidental.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Shafi'i didn't bloom.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:27.000
He's fast. From that double-touch feint, he'll go here.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:32.000
You ready?

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:34.000
Era's turn!

00:00:37.000 --> 00:00:40.000
I'm in behind. You really are perfect, Bajira.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:45.000
This'll work with our style of soccer. We can slice through them!

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Are you serious? How is he here?

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:02.000
You're the best!

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
A superb clearance by Oliver Aiku!

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.000
That play he made just now...

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:18.000
From where he was, he could see everyone's position on the field...

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:20.000
And where the pass might land.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:27.000
He assessed the situation in an instant, and ran to the most likely danger point without hesitation.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.000
The same reflexes I want to use to score.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:31.000
He's using them to defend against one.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:35.000
His field of vision, his brain, his physical abilities...

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:37.000
This guy's on a whole other level.

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:39.000
Nothing like what I faced.

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:43.000
When you talk about a real defender...

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:44.000
He is him.

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:46.000
Oliver Aiku!

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.000
Here comes the throw-in!

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:52.000
We've got to crush him.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.000
Or we'll never win this match!

00:01:59.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Here we come!

