B

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:26.000
B

00:02:26.000 --> 00:02:27.000
B

00:02:27.000 --> 00:02:29.000
B LeB that one bit.

00:02:31.060 --> 00:02:33.000
B external support for Link's mouth.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:35.000
You're gonna get stuck here, mate.

00:02:35.139 --> 00:02:37.139
I'm gonna beank at the erfolg.

00:02:37.139 --> 00:03:07.119
Thank you.

00:03:07.139 --> 00:03:37.119
Thank you.

00:03:37.139 --> 00:04:07.119
Thank you.

00:04:07.139 --> 00:04:37.120
Thank you.

00:04:37.139 --> 00:04:39.139
Thank you.

00:05:07.139 --> 00:05:09.240
Sweet goggles. I'm jealous.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.879
Hey, thanks, Pipsqueak.

00:05:17.759 --> 00:05:19.759
How'd you like La Bova?

00:05:20.399 --> 00:05:21.479
This way?

00:05:21.800 --> 00:05:23.819
You're faster than your data says.

00:05:24.120 --> 00:05:24.719
Hold on.

00:05:25.099 --> 00:05:26.079
I thought I passed him.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:28.979
He's one speedy defender.

00:05:30.219 --> 00:05:31.360
Over here?

00:05:32.219 --> 00:05:35.120
I'm not really the burly carnivorous type, you know.

00:05:35.680 --> 00:05:37.039
More of an herbivore

00:05:37.040 --> 00:05:38.080
with unmatched speed.

00:05:38.300 --> 00:05:38.560
Fat.

00:05:38.939 --> 00:05:40.000
You sure about that?

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:42.020
Because you're aggressive for a vegetarian.

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:45.260
No way. Yuki Miya's being tracked?

00:05:45.879 --> 00:05:46.879
You're here.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.140
He can't get past him.

00:05:49.400 --> 00:05:50.600
He's fast as lightning.

00:05:50.840 --> 00:05:52.620
Who in the hell is that fullback?

00:05:52.840 --> 00:05:53.680
Second ball!

00:05:53.939 --> 00:05:54.480
Got it.

00:05:55.580 --> 00:05:57.960
It's not going to be easy slicing through them.

00:05:58.379 --> 00:05:59.740
I'll control it and turn.

00:06:00.420 --> 00:06:01.540
Pure destruction.

00:06:02.540 --> 00:06:03.840
Mr. Super Controller,

00:06:03.840 --> 00:06:06.240
I ain't giving you any freedom out here.

00:06:07.040 --> 00:06:08.040
itter ditch me, rendition botratez.

00:06:08.700 --> 00:06:10.240
That press was so fast

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:12.000
and his core is something else.

00:06:12.379 --> 00:06:14.379
I can't face the goal to make a play.

00:06:15.040 --> 00:06:17.040
He stopped Noggy from using his weapon!

00:06:17.040 --> 00:06:17.900
Noggy...

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:19.180
He's strong.

00:06:19.640 --> 00:06:21.320
A real power-presser!

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:23.920
You could call me the Doberman.

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:26.140
What are you a guard dog?

00:06:26.439 --> 00:06:27.320
Yeah...

00:06:27.600 --> 00:06:29.759
And here comes my master now.

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:33.820
Thanks, Mio.

00:06:33.939 --> 00:06:34.900
You good boy.

00:06:35.860 --> 00:06:36.420
Ah.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:38.580
Aiku got it?

00:06:38.580 --> 00:06:41.040
They used a chain of plays to lock up the ball.

00:06:41.040 --> 00:06:43.040
So this is the U-20's defense.

00:06:43.040 --> 00:06:46.040
The Iron Wall Quartet!

00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.040
What's wrong, Blue Lock?

00:06:48.040 --> 00:06:49.040
You're not moving.

00:06:52.040 --> 00:06:53.040
They got us!

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:55.040
With just one pass from the back,

00:06:55.040 --> 00:06:57.040
they sent it straight to him!

00:06:59.040 --> 00:07:01.040
Sai Itoshi!

00:07:01.040 --> 00:07:04.040
Well, it's time for your debut.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:07.040
Show us what you got, genius.

00:07:09.040 --> 00:07:11.040
Looks like the ball has gone to Sai Itoshi.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:14.040
Now, let's see what Shoei has in store for us!

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.040
No!

00:07:15.040 --> 00:07:17.040
Pass it through all of them!

00:07:18.040 --> 00:07:20.040
Are you trying to peg me?

00:07:20.040 --> 00:07:22.040
This is what you all do!

00:07:22.040 --> 00:07:23.040
Not happening!

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:26.040
Not when we're hedging our bets in case of a counterattack.

00:07:27.040 --> 00:07:29.040
When Bajira moves up,

00:07:29.040 --> 00:07:31.040
I fall back into defense,

00:07:31.040 --> 00:07:33.040
allowing me to respond.

00:07:33.040 --> 00:07:34.040
I'll hold you up when you're down.

00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:35.040
With my speed!

00:07:36.040 --> 00:07:38.040
What? Passing it already?

00:07:38.040 --> 00:07:40.040
He reacted so fast!

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:42.040
He kicked the ball over 50 meters away

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:44.040
with an arching mid-speed pass!

00:07:45.040 --> 00:07:47.040
That's crazy hard to pull off!

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:51.040
Amazing.

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:54.040
Seems the universe has decided

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:56.040
I shall be your opponent, Mannequin Man.

00:07:56.040 --> 00:07:57.040
Oh, no.

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:59.040
Kitsune!

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:01.040
Very nice!

00:08:01.040 --> 00:08:03.040
Don't waste time, just send it forward!

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:06.040
Just as I expected.

00:08:06.040 --> 00:08:08.040
Go ahead and try it, short stack.

00:08:08.040 --> 00:08:09.040
As expected, huh?

00:08:09.040 --> 00:08:11.040
I could say the same thing about you!

00:08:13.040 --> 00:08:14.040
Oh, hell.

00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:17.040
Sai Itoshi's free in front of the goal!

00:08:17.040 --> 00:08:19.040
And he's within range!

00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:21.040
It's an attack pattern.

00:08:21.040 --> 00:08:23.040
One that begins and ends with him.

00:08:23.040 --> 00:08:26.040
They were setting up for a Katanachiyo counter.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:27.040
That's their objective!

00:08:27.040 --> 00:08:28.040
Niko!

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:29.040
I'm there!

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:32.039
Stop him shooting!

00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:33.039
I just need to buy one second!

00:08:33.039 --> 00:08:36.039
Because then, Chigiri will make it back!

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:37.039
Great save, Niko!

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:38.039
We pincered him!

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:40.039
We halted Sai Itoshi!

00:08:45.039 --> 00:08:47.039
He aimed between us!

00:08:47.039 --> 00:08:49.039
What an impressive looping pass!

00:08:50.039 --> 00:08:52.039
Just how far can this guy see?

00:08:52.039 --> 00:08:53.039
This one's in!

00:08:54.039 --> 00:08:55.039
Go, Lee!

00:08:55.039 --> 00:08:56.039
Uh-oh, I'm on!

00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:01.039
Fire away, Synapses!

00:09:01.039 --> 00:09:03.039
Here's my super-weapon!

00:09:03.039 --> 00:09:04.039
No reaction!

00:09:04.039 --> 00:09:05.039
Gagamaru...

00:09:05.039 --> 00:09:06.039
Oh!

00:09:06.039 --> 00:09:07.039
Shh!

00:09:07.039 --> 00:09:08.039
What?

00:09:08.039 --> 00:09:09.039
Nice, Gagamaru!

00:09:10.039 --> 00:09:11.039
Sai Itoshi's going for the ball!

00:09:11.039 --> 00:09:13.039
It's still in play!

00:09:13.039 --> 00:09:14.039
He's already running?

00:09:14.039 --> 00:09:15.039
Incoming!

00:09:15.039 --> 00:09:16.039
Watch for the cross!

00:09:19.039 --> 00:09:20.039
He doesn't have the angle.

00:09:20.039 --> 00:09:21.039
Good.

00:09:21.039 --> 00:09:22.039
We'll stop him!

00:09:27.039 --> 00:09:28.039
Huh?

00:09:29.039 --> 00:09:30.039
Huh?

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:35.039
Oh, ho!

00:09:44.039 --> 00:09:45.039
Incredible.

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:52.039
A line-drive shot from that position?

00:09:52.039 --> 00:09:57.039
Not only that, how many techniques did he deploy in the lead-up to that shot?

00:09:59.039 --> 00:10:01.039
He is in.

00:10:01.039 --> 00:10:02.039
Yes!

00:10:02.039 --> 00:10:03.039
And she scores!

00:10:03.039 --> 00:10:04.039
He scored a goal...

00:10:04.039 --> 00:10:05.039
He scores a 20-point shot.

00:10:05.039 --> 00:10:06.039
So it doesn't matter the score.

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:07.039
All of them stare to celebrate.

00:10:07.039 --> 00:10:08.039
Tickle!

00:10:08.039 --> 00:10:09.039
Oh, he did it.

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.039
Gave-and-tickle!

00:10:10.039 --> 00:10:11.039
So loud.

00:10:12.039 --> 00:10:15.959
We're playing the ultimate away game.

00:10:15.959 --> 00:10:18.000
Yeah, tough crowd.

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:19.980
Now I understand.

00:10:19.980 --> 00:10:28.480
This whole match is a performance, and he's the lead actor.

00:10:30.439 --> 00:10:31.439
Abergrich!

00:10:32.039 --> 00:10:37.039
Sire! Sire! Sire! Sire! Sire!

00:10:37.039 --> 00:10:39.039
Then you have the Blue Lock team.

00:10:42.039 --> 00:10:44.039
Nothing but a bunch of foils.

00:10:45.039 --> 00:10:47.039
To make him look better.

00:10:48.039 --> 00:10:53.039
No one, not a single person in this stadium cares about us.

00:10:57.039 --> 00:10:58.039
Don't get overwhelmed.

00:10:58.039 --> 00:11:03.039
Stay focused and keep your eyes on me.

00:11:04.039 --> 00:11:10.039
90 minutes from now, I'm going to turn their cheers into pitiful wails.

00:11:11.039 --> 00:11:12.039
It's me.

00:11:28.039 --> 00:11:30.039
No, that was an amazing shot!

00:11:30.039 --> 00:11:32.039
More than that, it was a super goal!

00:11:32.039 --> 00:11:33.039
Hands off, chump.

00:11:35.039 --> 00:11:36.039
Three chances.

00:11:38.039 --> 00:11:40.039
That's the number of times I could have taken a shot.

00:11:41.039 --> 00:11:42.039
But I held back.

00:11:42.039 --> 00:11:46.039
Used up time and energy passing the ball to you losers instead.

00:11:48.039 --> 00:11:52.039
That piece of garbage Mr. Golem Monkey could have made with ease.

00:11:52.039 --> 00:11:54.039
Pissed me off, so I took the shot.

00:11:55.039 --> 00:11:57.039
Garbage... Monkey...

00:11:58.039 --> 00:11:59.039
Come on now.

00:12:00.039 --> 00:12:02.039
You've got to admit, their goalie's playing pretty good too.

00:12:03.039 --> 00:12:04.039
Huh?

00:12:04.039 --> 00:12:07.039
A striker's only as valuable as the number of goals that he makes.

00:12:07.039 --> 00:12:13.039
If you're being outscored by a midfielder like me, then in my book, you might as well not be called a striker at all.

00:12:14.039 --> 00:12:16.039
Being a prodigy's made you kind of jaded.

00:12:16.039 --> 00:12:19.039
In that case, how about you tell us how many strikers there are in Japan?

00:12:20.039 --> 00:12:22.039
The whole reason we're playing this match is to find out.

00:12:23.039 --> 00:12:26.039
Don't mess up again, you talentless primate.

00:12:28.039 --> 00:12:32.039
Relax, guys. The game's only just begun. But yeah...

00:12:33.039 --> 00:12:35.039
No more screwing up.

00:12:35.039 --> 00:12:41.039
Yeah, I know. This is my team. Not that guy's.

00:12:45.039 --> 00:12:48.039
Well damn. And I saved two.

00:12:48.039 --> 00:12:50.039
A stylish save at that.

00:12:50.039 --> 00:12:51.039
Your reaction time, sir.

00:12:51.039 --> 00:12:54.039
Glam, you made me proud.

00:12:54.039 --> 00:12:57.039
I'm still confused. How could he score from over there?

00:12:57.039 --> 00:13:00.039
They've got sturdy defense and a rapid offense.

00:13:00.039 --> 00:13:05.039
With Sai Itoshi, the U-20s have shot up to an even more incredible level.

00:13:05.039 --> 00:13:06.039
I noticed.

00:13:08.039 --> 00:13:11.039
First, they tighten up their defense with those four.

00:13:12.039 --> 00:13:16.039
And then, when we can't find a decisive way through, they steal the ball.

00:13:17.039 --> 00:13:21.039
That's when the rapid counterattack initiated by Sai Itoshi kicks off.

00:13:22.039 --> 00:13:26.039
This is how the U-20 team plays the game.

00:13:27.039 --> 00:13:29.039
So how do we break them?

00:13:30.039 --> 00:13:34.039
We made sure to drill that strategy into them at the final training camp.

00:13:34.039 --> 00:13:35.039
But it's not working.

00:13:35.039 --> 00:13:38.039
We're going to be okay, right?

00:13:38.039 --> 00:13:40.039
It's not like this was unexpected.

00:13:40.039 --> 00:13:43.039
Huh? You sound a little nonchalant.

00:13:43.039 --> 00:13:46.039
Practice is merely practice. Nothing more.

00:13:47.039 --> 00:13:52.039
It's good for acquiring fundamental skills, but not for deploying those skills under pressure.

00:13:53.039 --> 00:13:55.039
It applies to any field.

00:13:55.039 --> 00:14:01.039
Someone can perform well during practice, but can't pull off the actual performance.

00:14:02.039 --> 00:14:07.039
Oh, I've experienced that myself. Like making mistakes during a piano recital.

00:14:07.039 --> 00:14:09.039
Precisely right.

00:14:09.039 --> 00:14:14.039
The decisive difference between training and a real performance is stress.

00:14:15.039 --> 00:14:17.039
The environment.

00:14:17.039 --> 00:14:19.039
Your opponents.

00:14:19.039 --> 00:14:21.039
One's own physical condition.

00:14:22.039 --> 00:14:24.039
Your mental state.

00:14:24.039 --> 00:14:26.039
Tension in the muscles.

00:14:26.039 --> 00:14:28.039
Stagnant thought processes.

00:14:28.039 --> 00:14:33.039
When it comes to competition, these factors can drag you into a negative spiral.

00:14:34.039 --> 00:14:37.039
Things never play out exactly the way you planned.

00:14:37.039 --> 00:14:41.039
But there is always a surefire way to break through that uncertainty.

00:14:42.039 --> 00:14:43.039
Improvising.

00:14:44.039 --> 00:14:47.039
What? Then you're not going to give them any instructions?

00:14:47.039 --> 00:14:49.039
You can't just sit here and watch them fail.

00:14:49.039 --> 00:14:51.039
Just shut up and trust them.

00:14:51.039 --> 00:14:53.039
Our little egoists know the score.

00:14:54.039 --> 00:14:55.039
They will perform.

00:15:00.039 --> 00:15:04.039
I can't find the missing piece we need to break through their defense.

00:15:04.039 --> 00:15:08.039
To me, they're formidable enemies with unknown potential.

00:15:08.039 --> 00:15:09.039
But...

00:15:09.039 --> 00:15:12.039
Stay focused. And keep your eyes on me.

00:15:13.039 --> 00:15:15.039
What I have to do is clear.

00:15:15.039 --> 00:15:17.039
Get rid of any useless thoughts.

00:15:17.039 --> 00:15:20.039
Focus only on this moment.

00:15:20.039 --> 00:15:23.039
And consolidate all of my skills into this move with Rin!

00:15:24.039 --> 00:15:29.039
No matter how much you pass around the midfield, it's hopeless.

00:15:29.039 --> 00:15:31.039
Yep. Bet you're confused.

00:15:31.039 --> 00:15:34.039
There's not a single player to kick to. Not one.

00:15:34.039 --> 00:15:37.039
Get some sleep, panda eyes.

00:15:40.039 --> 00:15:42.039
He's making shorter passes.

00:15:43.039 --> 00:15:45.039
Is he adjusting our attacking pattern?

00:15:46.039 --> 00:15:48.039
So you decided to ditch the triangle.

00:15:48.039 --> 00:15:50.039
Shut everything else out.

00:15:50.039 --> 00:15:52.039
Stick with the Nien's vision.

00:15:52.039 --> 00:15:54.039
And go off!

00:15:54.039 --> 00:15:56.039
Now they're passing it faster?

00:15:59.039 --> 00:16:01.039
I can't get a read on the two of them.

00:16:01.039 --> 00:16:04.039
Number 11 is constantly running around 10,

00:16:04.039 --> 00:16:07.039
which is dramatically boosting the ladder's options.

00:16:09.039 --> 00:16:10.039
Crap.

00:16:10.039 --> 00:16:12.039
A heal pass? Here?

00:16:12.039 --> 00:16:14.039
They drew us out.

00:16:14.039 --> 00:16:16.039
Yoo-hoo.

00:16:16.039 --> 00:16:19.039
That Linka play was making me jealous.

00:16:19.039 --> 00:16:21.039
So now you're both free to go up front.

00:16:21.039 --> 00:16:22.039
Is that it?

00:16:22.039 --> 00:16:24.039
I like that plan.

00:16:25.039 --> 00:16:27.039
There are two center backs behind Nagi.

00:16:27.039 --> 00:16:29.039
It's a three on two.

00:16:29.039 --> 00:16:31.039
Which means we have them outnumbered.

00:16:31.039 --> 00:16:33.039
And a gold chance.

00:16:33.039 --> 00:16:35.039
From here on out,

00:16:35.039 --> 00:16:37.039
I'll follow my ego!

00:16:37.039 --> 00:16:39.039
So now they're moving apart?

00:16:39.039 --> 00:16:41.039
I don't understand this combo.

00:16:41.039 --> 00:16:43.039
But they're not getting through us!

00:16:45.039 --> 00:16:48.039
Those are some pretty great moves, little burglar.

00:16:48.039 --> 00:16:50.039
All right. Gimme.

00:16:51.039 --> 00:16:53.039
Uh-uh. I see you there.

00:16:53.039 --> 00:16:55.039
Readventure!

00:16:59.039 --> 00:17:00.039
They got through!

00:17:00.039 --> 00:17:02.039
